Christensen- &ldquo;I did the hard work &amp; kept the ball in play, but then I made a bad decision. As a defender you get punished by mistakes, I won&rsquo;t be dwelling on it or letting it get to me.<br />
<br />
I made a mistake, I must learn from it and make sure it doesn&rsquo;t happen again.&rdquo;

Hazard - &ldquo;We should have won the game, but when you play against this kind of team you have to be focused 100%.<br />
<br />
We made one mistake but if we&rsquo;d scored more goals the mistake doesn&rsquo;t count, so a draw is a bad result for us because now we have to play in Barcelona.&quot;
